      "text_span_id": "intro_2",
      "text": "examples being oral biofilms ('dental plaque') and biofilms involved in a variety of pathological conditions like for instance osteomyelitis, chronic otitis media, the infected diabetic foot, chronic bacterial prostatitis or in biomaterial-associated infections",
